- DO NOT USE previous gem versions before 1.3.20, they can be used to execute arbitrary commands on your server !

- publish the gem :
	gem build admin_tools_ennder.gemspec

- test :
	C.f. rails/1_gems/test_gems_ennder_rails3
	rake test

- publication :
	curl -u qrush https://rubygems.org/api/v1/api_key.yaml >~/.gem/credentials; chmod 0600 ~/.gem/credentials

	gem push admin_tools_ennder-1.3.12.gem
